{"tid":1189834,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【五日四夜】【人車合一】加拿大洛磯山脈之旅","createTime":"2019-06-07T04:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T05:21:56.000Z","uid":54344,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"011d8e66b62fb86d30c13d990aae86a83a4daaac","tid":1189834,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:05:16.000Z","msg":"講明先，我呢五日所去嘅景點同行程僅供參考，我絕對唔建議大家跟住我黎行。原因之一係呢個旅程完全唔係我plan嘅，我淨係負責揸車同食曬啲餸，我都係當連登係facebook記錄下嘅姐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相就好多都係用部nexus 5影，鏡頭已經裂鳩咗，質素差啲多多見諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩問題隨便問，答到就答。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，譯名我都係靠wikipedia同google map，所以大家有咩指正，我無任歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n我前幾日有啲親戚黎玩，佢地好想話去rocky mountains打個圈，咁一場黎到，兩老就梗係帶佢地去玩啦。五日冇理由要我老豆揸足全程架嘛，來回千幾二千公里好傷神，我老母就夾硬拖咗我落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。。。孝子如我點推啊，死死地氣應承咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅行程大約係咁：<br />\n<br />\nD1：Vancouver -&gt; Kamloops -&gt; Golden<br />\nD2：Golden -&gt; Lake Louise -&gt; Calgary<br />\nD3：Calgary -&gt; Banff -&gt; Canmore<br />\nD4：Canmore -&gt; Columbia Icefield -&gt; Revelstoke<br />\nD5：Revelstoke -&gt; Kelowna -&gt; Vancouver<br />\n<br />\nI repeat，on9行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸到仆街（我），跟住停一陣，跟住又揸到仆街（多數都係我）。<br />\n<br />\nAnyway，出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eptbMRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeptbMRC.png&h=ea16cfca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九點鐘出發，第一程係我老豆揸，我就爭取時間補補眠。訓咗一陣（個幾鐘），話咁快就到Hope。Hope係Lower Mainland（低陸平原）嘅最東端，過咗就係Hopeless開始進入Cascade Mountains<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j9XfVqV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj9XfVqV.png&h=7b11feb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n距離Kamloops（甘露市）仲有二百幾公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.britannica.com/74/112874-004-A4866C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.britannica.com%2F74%2F112874-004-A4866C24.jpg&h=775a4e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地大多數都係揸Tran-Canada Highway（橫加公路），顧名思義就係一條橫跨加拿大嘅公路。雖然如此，呢條【公路】並唔係聯邦政府管理，而係各省自己管理，所以喺每個省都係唔同名，例如喺BC同Alberta等西部省分就會叫Highway 1，而東部就有其他名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mn1ykAj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMn1ykAj.jpg&h=3377fc61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好沙塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/7qFvOvK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F7qFvOvK.png&h=4a1161b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n揸車揸到咁上下，係時候落車入油同揸揸水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XVoJgMO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXVoJgMO.png&h=d8dd439b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁somewhere else唔係真係somewhere else嘅，呢度係Dogwood Valley<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/8AUc5MI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F8AUc5MI.png&h=b0f123cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MKH1EnB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMKH1EnB.png&h=139c48a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gbDHggh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgbDHggh.png&h=37fc9125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廁所奇遇，睇真啲原來好貼心，由左起分別係condom，鹹相，偉哥同ky。不過係我就擺返兩部賣飛機杯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fJCsG37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfJCsG37.png&h=d0b83fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家去完洗手間就到我坐駕駛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1pBEfYo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1pBEfYo.png&h=1b33931f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CZWWfm1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCZWWfm1.png&h=c8435ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n揸咗一個鐘，前面塞車，啲人仲要落曬車。後尾先知前面加固緊啲山坡，單線雙程行車緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4F1D6c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4F1D6c5.png&h=6cbb604e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBC省有差唔多二百種蝴蝶，恕我孤陋寡聞，真係唔識係咩蝴蝶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GSGtfS0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGSGtfS0.png&h=6f45c4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於我揸車嘅關係，我地fast-forward到下一站，Kamloops Costco！兩點幾，又是時候入油同醫下肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGas price: 136.9<br />\nMileage count: 252km<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CS45Uyd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCS45Uyd.png&h=778c12e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QmZy4wE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQmZy4wE.png&h=d3c5e991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎Costco係得hotdog食，唉是但<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗食指數：5/10<br />\n條腸好能鹹，不過$1.5就算你啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h0Fqa3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh0Fqa3f.png&h=80883ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u03RUDs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu03RUDs.png&h=33d6def4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下一手當然比返老豆揸啦，左邊就係Kamloops<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GajmfaJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGajmfaJ.png&h=6612d9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cymcapl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fcymcapl.jpg&h=61d3b7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n訓訓下，比我見到Last Spike個景點仔，大家又係落車影相嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLast Spike係加拿大太平洋鐵路連接卑詩省同東面其他省分嘅最後一口釘。喺1885年見證住太平洋鐵路嘅完工，亦都係實現咗聯邦政府對卑詩省加入加拿大聯邦嘅承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VM4cp9Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVM4cp9Y.png&h=225970d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然最後一口釘就梗係象徵意義大啲啦，百幾年來都唔知換咗幾多粒釘啦。咁但係每年夏天都會有人噴下漆扮下野嘅，不過噴到咁我覺得就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/koMtNnA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkoMtNnA.png&h=1c2e6400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冬天去嗰陣我都唔知喺度睇乜，隊長我看不到屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/B47eYko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FB47eYko.png&h=5343b66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完粒釘，又係揸車時間，呢次我地就直踩Golden。呢度已經係Rocky Mountains嘅範圍，所以後面啲山都係洛磯山脈之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMileage count: 447km"},{"pid":"e630efddf221b377919e6fd89d75147ee77c4657","tid":1189834,"uid":54344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"未update之前大家可以睇下其他19野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1158637/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1158637/</a><br />\n已完，又係加國，不過係行山post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/107449/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/107449/</a><br />\n兩年前爛咗尾，你當我淨係去咗Scotland啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cceed44393b7cdf4ce102d46f997da0bed5e4913","tid":1189834,"uid":29464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"813b90ac3dbf5d603f2da7e6ac22670662611815","tid":1189834,"uid":144090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"爛尾?"},{"pid":"cec449849f5bcd27cd0ca1d08dab766254c52dff","tid":1189834,"uid":54344,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"813b90ac3dbf5d603f2da7e6ac22670662611815","tid":1189834,"uid":144090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"爛尾?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T17:39:23.000Z","msg":"宜家香港水深火熱，國難當前，點有心機打文啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed7d37ac904116909bde353b4906c44ccddb3d5","tid":1189834,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"我都揸過車行呢個旅程, 不過只去到BANFF 同LAKE LOUISE<br />\n揸到HIHI <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBANFF 同LAKE LOUISE 係靚的"},{"pid":"e494e4405f68f7e71609c8190b40110a5d4ad6ee","tid":1189834,"uid":177727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"無update左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43f1f95424a2225a20458560158440e0df0af8c","tid":1189834,"uid":128127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T01:03:40.000Z","msg":"幾年前揸過去Banff Jasper玩咗幾日 覺得Moraine Lake仲靚過Lake Louise<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾日經過Jasper嗰陣先啱啱落完雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cd64b4a05ffb6bb9c743a7dffefa896c11ed05","tid":1189834,"uid":20371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344c34201e345cb044e0b2121266a19160dfbbd7","tid":1189834,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e494e4405f68f7e71609c8190b40110a5d4ad6ee","tid":1189834,"uid":177727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:53:45.000Z","msg":"無update左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:35:09.000Z","msg":"好快有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93baa6bcb7057db18a9c7ca1c13b2d63282ebd46","tid":1189834,"uid":54344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q6RE7m7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq6RE7m7.png&h=e83253bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n間野原來係間法院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ocieeai.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Focieeai.png&h=a9e0e779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一手就梗係留返比老豆揸啦，我就繼續訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8jBgeqy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8jBgeqy.jpg&h=f09a31bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲山路唔開山劈石都過唔到，真係前人種樹，後人乘涼；前人鋪路，後人揸車。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LfPnV4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLfPnV4r.jpg&h=48269ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n進入Yoho National Park（幽鶴國家公園）<br />\n題外話，我覺得呢個譯名拍得住Yosemite譯優勝美地，雖然個名係九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZhmIlfC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZhmIlfC.jpg&h=638364ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隊長我看不到屎。。。<br />\nAll vehicles proceeding on this road require a valid National Park vehicle permit<br />\n由於入咗國家公園嘅範圍，所有車都要買飛，或者有張通行證。而啲貨車啊嗰啲穿過國家公園範圍都要申請permit。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KMwH6zm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKMwH6zm.jpg&h=19f04cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似呢張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FjR6V8P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFjR6V8P.jpg&h=738acd78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CsIuyP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCsIuyP5.jpg&h=377dec05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是日第一個景點：Emerald Lake <br />\nSupposedly 嗰湖係好撚藍，不過相機唔爭氣。唔緊要，回程嗰陣都有經過，而且有單反加持，大家等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nb7OR75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fnb7OR75.jpg&h=ac73cee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湖邊有幾間lodge，唔洗審肯定貴到仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3ZLJnZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3ZLJnZP.jpg&h=029f6847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本上個個公園，唔理國家級定省級嘅，都係唔比玩無人機，一定係有啲撚屌做壞曬規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/V7ogjO7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FV7ogjO7.jpg&h=540bf61d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有個trading post仔賣下紀念品同租船。一個鐘七十蚊加紙，圍起四舊水港紙，一頸血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rhSeBWd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrhSeBWd.jpg&h=774d76b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左手邊就係間trading post，過橋就係啲lodge，成個Emerald Lake就係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2bGtttS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2bGtttS.jpg&h=3d543c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOn the way out離開Emerald Lake，歡迎大家黎到Natural Bridge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sWZLkIb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsWZLkIb.jpg&h=bb169c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n背撚曬光屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hrsPZYF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhrsPZYF.jpg&h=4b7413be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借用下人地嘅相，真係有條橋架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource：jstottphotography<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OYAvBLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOYAvBLt.jpg&h=34974add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aUeyORz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaUeyORz.jpg&h=a46bca5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有條橋，點會冇河呢？呢條踢馬河顧名思義就係當年有條傻西瓜比隻馬踢咗落河，連帶附近個隘口都叫做Kicking Horse Pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/THlznKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTHlznKd.jpg&h=b5b3c56e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條河成日望落去都係好濁咁，係因為有大量嘅石灰岩同埋唔同嘅沖積物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rn7hM0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRn7hM0F.jpg&h=88561908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n離開Emerald Lake同Natural Bridge，我地繼續向東行（姐係轉左）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ba8ajmW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fba8ajmW.jpg&h=93a4a640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uKwB6BX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuKwB6BX.jpg&h=6333e570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一路都係崇山峻嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1DNI7f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1DNI7f8.jpg&h=56c3db54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比動物行嘅天橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7epmrBl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7epmrBl.jpg&h=7d56f9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於時間嘅關係，我地已經黎到是日景點二：Lake Louise<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vxGqDEh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvxGqDEh.jpg&h=13503142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ymIWIel.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FymIWIel.jpg&h=98b1011e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係同大家講係要黎下，最好就冬天同夏天都黎一轉，兩種唔同體會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/naXatyV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnaXatyV.jpg&h=95e2f9dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過預咗係會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kgongnj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKgongnj.jpg&h=59d34899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KnLGzgR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKnLGzgR.jpg&h=64e30ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山風凌厲，將湖面嘅冰吹到呢邊岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u6O8iPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu6O8iPI.jpg&h=ea7b3580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影咗兩張相之後，老豆同我講原來午餐係喺間酒店high tea？！話係班親戚請下我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/V5Z1p7B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FV5Z1p7B.jpg&h=b791fa3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ivjrmBS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FivjrmBS.jpg&h=c9620387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mFzrmOT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmFzrmOT.jpg&h=20256201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tQcjywV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtQcjywV.jpg&h=5db8b769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IMKLTyy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIMKLTyy.jpg&h=4d0a573d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iJmTtuu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiJmTtuu.jpg&h=e0e297a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗食指數：0/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五星級酒店high tea啊大佬，好似好high class咁，又煙三文魚又龍蝦。幾好食之餘仲好撚飽，邊度狗食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pb6qvky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fpb6qvky.jpg&h=4c014d12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Bo5MTEw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBo5MTEw.jpg&h=006a3eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eyLb2eg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeyLb2eg.jpg&h=32159264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完就梗係行下鬆鬆腳，巧遇花鼠明星俱樂部真鼠版，好肥好撚cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aR0H3Ql.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaR0H3Ql.jpg&h=fb0814b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個角度就藍好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rRUzHGW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrRUzHGW.jpg&h=28f8ee74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個角度又唔同色，好難捉摸啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay2待續..."},{"pid":"2ec5faab790c15d42a85aa703a8bd674ea10e39f","tid":1189834,"uid":54344,"like":0,